name: Applique YOUR shirt
description:
This listing is to have Charming-Ollie applique a shirt that YOU send in. I will put a fun applique of your choosing (available fabrics may vary) on a shirt that you send in to me. Again - I DO NOT provide the shirt. 

Search for inspiration @ https://www.facebook.com/charmingollie

Please leave applique(s) requested in comments and I will get with you on the address where shirts should be sent. 

Thanks for looking!
